title: FL Studio 12.0.2 with Key Reg OSX
description:
FL Studio 12.0.2 With Key Reg. OSX


1. Install flstudio-12.0.2_OSX_Installer.
2. UN-RAR [AAFWORLD]Image-Line FL Studio 12.0.1 Reg Key (password: AFFWORLD)
3. Launch FL Studio.  (If you're using GateKeeper "right-click" FL Studio and choose [Open], then when the system says "FL Studio is not from an Identified Developer" click [Open] again.  If you don't see the [Open] button, you didn't "right-click" on the icon, try again.)  When FL Studio first launches you will see nothing for about 2 minutes, then a splash-screen that says "DEMO".
4.Go to Menu "FL Studio" > Register FL Studio.
5.Click on [Select Key File]. Choose "FLRegKey.reg".


NJOY!!!

PLEASE SEED
